Your Honor, I urge you to consider these mitigating factors as you deliberate on an appropriate sentence for my offense. I understand the seriousness of my actions and the need to make amends. I am willing to do whatever it takes to make this situation right and to demonstrate my dedication to being a responsible member of society.

